{"tid":1984352,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[皮膚科]玫瑰痤瘡？","createTime":"2020-04-22T11:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T10:09:54.000Z","uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47b415846cf8a9dddb3019e591ba21da63617021","tid":1984352,"uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"跪求大家介紹好嘅皮膚科醫生！！<br />\n<br />\n今年四月頭無啦啦大爆發，呢排好少出街應該唔關口罩事。<br />\n<br />\n宜家頭早起身 <span style=\"color: orange;\">塊臉會有幾粒膿但好細粒</span>，唔似係瘡，因為平時谷m生瘡係好大粒，兩邊塊面紅但唔係好嚴重，小小小小痛，唔痕，<span style=\"color: orange;\">摸落好粗唔滑，宜家去到眼兩邊都有一粒粒嘅野</span>，但嗰啲就眼睇唔出。<br />\n<br />\n前排轉咗用卸妝油，本身用卸妝水，護膚品都好似太潤，唔知關唔關事，如果係咁轉用咩會好啲？定呢排淨用清水乜都唔好搽住？<br />\n<br />\n究竟我係轉季敏感定<span style=\"color: orange;\">玫瑰痤瘡</span>定其他病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹本身轉季會生小小濕疹<br />\n<br />\n萬分感激！！！！！好人一生平安！！！！！！"},{"pid":"43a97ba36fd7b80efc66494309da6d0b995cdd4d","tid":1984352,"uid":155725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"da26ef06aefe780d18736ee57906a0a497790dbc","tid":1984352,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"Same 我上年起到宜家"},{"pid":"14a07512479cef459403acf9b0c121960afb531b","tid":1984352,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=69498565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=e6aa463f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE戒色圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA%2Fvideos&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=f4388d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n香港戒色論壇<br />\n<a href=\"http://noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnoj1314.258club.com&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=a12327bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n<br />\n秦東魁老師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLyVAEphpUDM&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=0b5fa524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM</a><br />\n<br />\n戒色吧<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Ff%3Fkw%3D%25BD%25E4%25C9%25AB&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=0e3658a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知：<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人生三寶精氣神，精少造成氣短，也就是身體差，容貌醜、容易累。氣短又造成神衰，也就是腦袋發矇，記憶力差，頭痛沒精神。辦事學習效率低，別人說話也理解不了，或者理解很慢。<br />\n<br />\n所以恢復的關鍵在養精，從徹底戒櫓開始留住精液，平時早睡早起養精神，鍛鍊選擇慢跑可補氣。"},{"pid":"186581fed20746bd97b205c72d61538d80236a9c","tid":1984352,"uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da26ef06aefe780d18736ee57906a0a497790dbc","tid":1984352,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"Same 我上年起到宜家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"我諗住過幾日去睇中環李祖祺，但好似態度麻麻，希望係effective"},{"pid":"35f1530f6f889f7d475a189332b6f407cc662262","tid":1984352,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186581fed20746bd97b205c72d61538d80236a9c","tid":1984352,"uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da26ef06aefe780d18736ee57906a0a497790dbc","tid":1984352,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"Same 我上年起到宜家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"我諗住過幾日去睇中環李祖祺，但好似態度麻麻，希望係effective"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"試下一兩個禮拜剩係用清水洗面 睇下咩情況<br />\n有可能係敏感姐"},{"pid":"c8200057dcf2ef5db35006122ada6d2427c2338d","tid":1984352,"uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f1530f6f889f7d475a189332b6f407cc662262","tid":1984352,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186581fed20746bd97b205c72d61538d80236a9c","tid":1984352,"uid":305353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da26ef06aefe780d18736ee57906a0a497790dbc","tid":1984352,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"Same 我上年起到宜家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:03:06.